          "acceptedAnswer": {
            "@type": "Answer",
            "text": "The best stocks for beginners with little money are typically those that offer lower nominal share prices, allowing you to buy whole shares, or companies available through brokers that offer fractional shares. Blue-chip companies with long histories of stability are common starting points."
