          "name": "Are penny stocks good for beginners?",
          "acceptedAnswer": {
            "@type": "Answer",
            "text": "No. Penny stocks are highly volatile and often lack transparency. Beginners should stick to established, publicly traded companies on major exchanges rather than speculative penny stocks."
